reviews.comment: I felt like this place was trying too hard. Some of my favorite dishes are no longer available. The photos of the food were appetizing and palpable, but didn't live up to the hype. Satisfactory experience, will come again.

reviews.comment: I felt like this place wasn't trying at all. I shouldn't have to pay good money to be served vegetables from a can. This place is very dumpy and in a serious need of a fresh paint job. Seriously, how difficult is it to get a clean glass around here? This food will start the zombie apocalypse. Stay away!
